<%= provide(:body_id, 'index') %>
<%= provide(:result, '报表查看') %>

<div class="container-fluid content-wrapper">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <div class="hero-unit">
        <button type="button" class="close hidden-phone" data-dismiss="alert">&times;</button>
        <h1>选择查询日期</h1>

        <p>
          本系统报表可以按次、日、周、月进行报表查看，可以指定日期进行下载相关报表，报表评估数据根据相关评分标准生成。
          如修改了相应的评分标准，不影响已生成的报表数据，只对往后的报表数据有影响，如对结果有异议，可申请核对。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <ul class="breadcrumb">
        <li>
          <a href="/">
            <i class="radmin-icon radmin-home"></i>
            首页
          </a>
          <span class="divider">/</span>
        </li>
        <li class="active">
          <a href="/reports">
            <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
            测试评分报表
          </a>
          <span class="divider">/</span>
        </li>
        <li class="active">
          <i class="radmin-icon radmin-file"></i>
          选择日周月报表
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p></p>

  <%= form_tag('date2time_report', :method => 'get', class: 'well form-horizontal') do %>
    <div class="control-group pull-left">
      <label class="control-label" for="dp1"></label>

      <div class="controls">
        <div class="input-prepend input-append">
          <span class="add-on">日 期</span>
          <input id="dp1" class="span7" type="text" size="16" name="date">
          <span class="add-on"><i class="icon-calendar"></i></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    点数
    <%= select_tag :ds, options_from_collection_for_select(@ds, :first, :last), class: 'span2' -%>
    <%= submit_tag('查 询', class: 'btn btn-info span2') %>
  <% end %>

  <p></p>

  <%= form_tag('time_report.csv', :method => 'get', class: 'well form-horizontal') do %>
    <div class="control-group pull-left">
      <label class="control-label" for="dp2"></label>

      <div class="controls">
        <div class="input-prepend input-append">
          <span class="add-on">日 期</span>
          <input id="dp2" class="span7" type="text" size="16" name="date">
          <span class="add-on"><i class="icon-calendar"></i></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    点数
    <%= select_tag :ds, options_from_collection_for_select(@ds, :first, :last), class: 'span2' -%>
    <%= submit_tag('下 载', class: 'btn btn-info span2') %>
  <% end %>

  <p></p>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <h4 class="title">名言警句</h4>

      <div class="squiggly-border"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span12">
      <blockquote>
        <p>
          Etiam varius erat in nisl egestas id auctor lacus consectetur.
          Ut dui risus, auctor a malesuada volutpat, tempus sit amet arcu.
        </p>
        <small class="pull-right">Jane Doe via Mobile</small>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>






